Issue: Desktop agent output auto-scrolls too aggressively and shows worker JSON as raw text.

Symptoms:
- While agent output is streaming, the message list always jumps to the bottom.
- Worker output appears as raw JSON instead of readable progress/report details.

Evidence:
- renderer.js renderMessages set messageList.scrollTop = messageList.scrollHeight after every render.
- activity.json for RUN-20260708-172407466Z shows agent_text containing concatenated arckit-worker-report/v1 JSON objects.
- The same activity also contains structured reports under agents[].report and activity.reports from runtime.worker_report.completed.
- raw-events.jsonl shows codex.agent_message.delta streaming individual JSON characters for worker reports.

Conclusion:
- The scroll behavior is caused by unconditional bottom scrolling during message re-render.
- The JSON display is caused by treating worker report JSON delta as generic Codex output even though structured report data is already available.

Fix applied:
- renderer.js now tracks whether the message list is at the bottom.
- renderMessages scrolls to bottom only when the list was already bottom-stuck; otherwise it restores the previous scrollTop.
- Project/chat/run switches reset bottom sticking because they are new contexts.
- renderer.js now parses historical arckit-worker-report/v1 JSON text into report cards when possible.
- renderer.js hides raw agent JSON when an agent already has a structured report.
- desktop-run-manager.mjs no longer appends worker codex.agent_message.delta JSON chunks into activity.agent_text.
- desktop-run-manager.mjs parses completed worker agentMessage JSON into agent.report.
- renderer.js hides legacy worker JSON streams when structured activity.reports are available.

Verification:
- node --check runtime/arckit-runtime/desktop/renderer/renderer.js passed.
- node --check runtime/arckit-runtime/src/desktop-run-manager.mjs passed.
- npm run check in runtime/arckit-runtime passed.
- Saved RUN-20260708-172407466Z activity has 5 structured activity.reports.
- Saved RUN-20260708-172407466Z activity has structured agents[].report for all 5 workers; historical agent_text fragments are no longer needed for UI rendering.

Temporary instrumentation:
- None added.
